{"tid":935510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11歲女誤服母熬中藥山豆根湯　腦中毒致語言及肢體能力如嬰兒","createTime":"2018-12-10T05:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T20:52:08.000Z","uid":13468,"like":156,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"f1be979aa9ce487b9e0e82392164156a4c4043ac","tid":935510,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"河南11歲女誤服母熬中藥山豆根湯　腦中毒致語言及肢體能力如嬰兒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據內地《大河報》12月8日報道，文文母親稱：「我真的不知道山豆根有毒，原來我自己也煮水喝過，想著它可以治嗓子疼，誰知道女兒喝了會中毒這麼深。」文文一家雖然四處求醫，但因患者腦損傷嚴重，基底節區嚴重受損，治療難度很高。<br />\n<br />\n文文目前已經能站起身，也能簡單交流，不過肢體運動和語言表達能力依然不如一個3至4個月大的嬰兒。<br />\n<br />\n有清熱解毒和消腫利咽功效<br />\n<br />\n河南中醫一附院藥學部副主任陳天朝說，山豆根在不少中藥處方中都會用到，有清熱解毒和消腫利咽之功效，但這種藥含有苦參堿，所以有毒性，因此處方用量一般控制在6克以內：「我們做過試驗，超過這個劑量會引起不良反應。」<br />\n<br />\n所謂不良反應包括頭暈和行走不穩，經應用激素治療後可望恢復正常，但嚴重中毒可以造成腦幹、小腦、基底節區及大腦皮層病變，這類症狀較難恢復。報道指河南鄭州藥店直接出售山豆根，但店方限制購買量不能超過10克。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2189146/org/452a6a74a78994e8c431347ca06ff4d4.jpg/JJ8J8QsCLRJsNaMtnAzUFqx7uSywFia_jVLtYI1S7WA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2189146%2Forg%2F452a6a74a78994e8c431347ca06ff4d4.jpg%2FJJ8J8QsCLRJsNaMtnAzUFqx7uSywFia_jVLtYI1S7WA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=2c7aef4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/268995/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%9711%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%AA%A4%E6%9C%8D%E6%AF%8D%E7%86%AC%E4%B8%AD%E8%97%A5%E5%B1%B1%E8%B1%86%E6%A0%B9%E6%B9%AF-%E8%85%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E8%87%B4%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80%E5%8F%8A%E8%82%A2%E9%AB%94%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E5%A6%82%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F268995%2F%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E5%258D%259711%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%258D%25E7%2586%25AC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2597%25A5%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25B1%2586%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%25B9%25AF-%25E8%2585%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%25E8%2587%25B4%25E8%25AA%259E%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%2582%25A2%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%25AC%25B0%25E5%2585%2592&d=3VF6E2gJR1D7OfX8qt8MeBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=20d05581\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/268995/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%9711%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%AA%A4%E6%9C%8D%E6%AF%8D%E7%86%AC%E4%B8%AD%E8%97%A5%E5%B1%B1%E8%B1%86%E6%A0%B9%E6%B9%AF-%E8%85%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E8%87%B4%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80%E5%8F%8A%E8%82%A2%E9%AB%94%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E5%A6%82%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92</a>"},{"pid":"4942b72ef4c5b3d3fa76f4b8d1a9f3972dc79d69","tid":935510,"uid":75610,"like":405,"dislike":7,"score":398,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"自然淘汰 個老母害死個女"},{"pid":"c61decb8c60449f2edd703869598077bb34b04b7","tid":935510,"uid":142384,"like":211,"dislike":4,"score":207,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"諗住整死個女唔洗養 依家出事啦"},{"pid":"bea9441cfbe43d41ce181909a625507fdf1701dd","tid":935510,"uid":131064,"like":540,"dislike":13,"score":527,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五千年傳統智慧</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6b1880705e22e4d0c2aea1fb9e8dcb473fa85af4","tid":935510,"uid":11148,"like":57,"dislike":211,"score":-154,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"我真的不知道山豆根有毒<br />\n<br />\n正常人都知中藥係有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7f5bf32fa51d9568a8459beab3d2f0f8d13d35","tid":935510,"uid":74278,"like":214,"dislike":97,"score":117,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"西藥都有好多服用過量會死人<br />\n唔好為反而反啦"},{"pid":"ccb0042f33f9899042add7dfb6937c9a166932a2","tid":935510,"uid":35630,"like":127,"dislike":5,"score":122,"quote":{"pid":"6b1880705e22e4d0c2aea1fb9e8dcb473fa85af4","tid":935510,"uid":11148,"like":57,"dislike":211,"score":-154,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"我真的不知道山豆根有毒<br />\n<br />\n正常人都知中藥係有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"。。。。。"},{"pid":"c44779ea978c44b79a6453fc7641dd5e62f927f0","tid":935510,"uid":13468,"like":167,"dislike":1,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:34:16.000Z","msg":"今年1月，河南南陽11歲女生文文（化名）放學後因為口渴，喝下媽媽泡的一碗山豆根水，內含約50克山豆根，隨後出現口角緊閉、頭暈嘔吐、手腳變形、抽搐等症狀，無法控制身體活動，後被醫院診斷為「中毒性腦病」。<br />\n有內媒引述醫生意見，指山豆根含有毒性，正常人飲用含有6克以上的山豆根水，身體就會出現不良反應，而文文所服山豆根湯超標8倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c95391e4c48870a9f13b944c0770cffb531eb6b","tid":935510,"uid":3549,"like":203,"dislike":3,"score":200,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"比起窮，on9更加唔應該生"},{"pid":"5edb1e13f2cae13af0eef4a544ed276fa48d0c5d","tid":935510,"uid":51720,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"我懷疑古代朝鮮，賜予死刑貴族或官員嘅「死藥」，<br />\n佢應該係其中一項成分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478df28c5e188856c8165b7b644777ae49f26808","tid":935510,"uid":156376,"like":10,"dislike":17,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"睇到張圖，今次真係笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f373d0b56848fa496a210768f6c494ccafd8ad","tid":935510,"uid":140928,"like":8,"dislike":38,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"又話中藥冇副作用? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c3752acd2ae45db9b4909ee8192a66254adc6e","tid":935510,"uid":35699,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"達爾文獎"},{"pid":"99ddb6c47f758ec86ec1b2f60c57